        <p>Ready to see your options? Get a personalized Medicare quote in about 60 seconds using our online tool, or call for a full comparison with a licensed local agent.</p>

        <h2>Quick Online Quote</h2>
        <p>Our Sunfire Matrix tool generates personalized plan estimates based on your zip code, medications, doctors, and preferred pharmacy. It shows Medicare Advantage, Part D, and supplemental options ranked by estimated total annual cost.</p>
        <p style="text-align:center;margin:1.5rem 0;">
