        <p>Available Medicare Advantage plans with monthly premiums, copays, and MOOP. Part D drug plans with estimated annual medication costs. Medigap quotes with monthly premiums by carrier. Doctor and hospital network confirmation. Extra benefits comparison (dental, vision, hearing, fitness).</p>

        <h2>Prefer to Talk to a Person?</h2>
        <p>Many Vernal residents prefer a conversation over an online tool — and that is perfectly fine. Call Rocco at <a href="tel:+14352195120">435-219-5120</a> for a personalized consultation. Bring your medication list and we can have your comparison done in about 15 minutes. Available Monday through Friday, 1 pm to 5 pm at Smith's Pharmacy (1080 W Hwy 40, Vernal) or by phone anytime during business hours. Saturday appointments available by request.</p>

        <h2>Completely Free — Always</h2>
        <p>Quotes, comparisons, and enrollment help are always free. We are compensated by insurance carriers, not by you. No pressure, no obligation.</p>

